---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact us
nav: contact
permalink: /contact/
description: Contact MM Group Engineering for ship repair and marine engineering enquiries.
---

<section class="page-hero page-hero--compact">
  <div class="content-width">
    <h1 class="page-hero__title">Contact us</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__lead">Reach out for quotations, technical questions, or project planning.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="content-width contact-grid">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <h2 class="contact-card__title">Direct</h2>
      <p class="contact-card__line">
        <strong>Email</strong><br>
        <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>
      </p>
      <p class="contact-card__line">
        <strong>Phone</strong><br>
        <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>
      </p>
      <p class="contact-card__line">
        <strong>Address</strong><br>
        {{ site.address }}
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card contact-card--note">
      <h2 class="contact-card__title">Next steps</h2>
      <p>
        Share vessel type, location, and a short scope. We will respond with availability and any documents we need for a firm proposal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
